    "We first generated patient networks using cosine similarity to define edges.",
    "We used different thresholds (0.98, 0.95, 0.94, 0.92, 0.90).",
    "In this case, an edge connects two nodes when the cosine similarity exceeds the threshold.",
    "We stopped at 0.90 since we reached a completely connected graph.",
    "Table 4 summarises the characteristics of the networks generated by using cosine similarity at different level of threshold."
